summary: 1965  was a common year starting on Friday of the Gregorian calendar.
full_text: 1965  was a common year starting on Friday  of the Gregorian calendar, the 1965th year of the Common Era  and Anno Domini  designations, the 965th year of the 2nd millennium, the 65th year of the 20th century, and the 6th year of the 1960s decade.
